        <Parent_String>optical instruments [300024585], equipment for science and technology [300024517], equipment by profession or discipline [300022241], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
